Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveGombe State Governor Inuwa Yahaya on Tuesday praised the APC for selecting Sen. Kashim Shettima, a former governor of Borno, as its vice presidential nominee.
Yahaya claimed that the choice will ensure the APC’s win in the general elections of 2023.
The Gombe Government House’s Director-General of Press Affairs, Mr. Ismaila Uba-Misilli, released a statement in Gombe stating the governor’s position.
He claimed that Shettima’s selection was a brilliant move that would help the party easily win the upcoming 2023 presidential elections.
